dc_title_s: Bureau of Assisted Living Regions, Wisconsin 2020
dc_description_s: This data represents Bureau of Assisted Living region boundaries for Wisconsin in 2020. [This dataset contains boundaries for the Bureau of Assisted Living regions. The Bureau of Assisted Living is within the Division of Quality Assurance and responsible for the regulation of assisted living providers. For more information please visit the Wisconsin Department of Health Services website: https://www.dhs.wisconsin.gov/dqa/bal-regionalmap.htm]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://data.dhsgis.wi.gov/datasets/c36cbdbb1b2042638f279ff2b23e6d84_11?geometry=-103.702%2C42.041%2C-75.951%2C47.494
